data.name: linkLabel1.ToolTip
data.value: By generating an authentication key, your server will be shown in the BeamMP client server list and players across the world will easily be able to join your server. Click the link to visit the key generator.

data.name: hideUpdtMsgChckB.ToolTip
data.value: Hides the periodic update message which notifies you of a new server version. You should really keep this on and always update as soon as possible. An update message will always appear at startup regardless.

data.name: sendErrorsChckB.ToolTip
data.value: If Send Errors is checked, the server will send helpful info about crashes and other issues back to the BeamMP developers. This info may include your config, who is on your server at the time of the error, and similar general information. This kind of data is vital in helping us diagnose and fix issues faster. This has no impact on server performance. You can opt-out of this system by unchecking this
